text.autoconfig.photosynthesis.title: Photosynthesis Config
text.autoconfig.photosynthesis.option.th:
When YES, Thirst is enabled. 
 (If on server, edit server config file manually, requires server restart)
text.autoconfig.photosynthesis.option.se:
When YES, Seasons is enabled. 
 (If on server, edit server config file manually, requires server restart)
text.autoconfig.photosynthesis.option.da:
Days per season. 
 (If on server, edit server config file manually, requires server restart)
text.autoconfig.photosynthesis.option.sp:
When YES Animals from egg spawn as baby. 
 Only Affects: Pig,Cow,Sheep,Chicken,Horse & Goats. 
 (If on server, edit server config file manually, requires server restart)
